Report Package Versions

Source: R/admiral_pkg_versions.R
admiral_pkg_versions.Rd

Function returns a string listing the packages and their versions.

Usage

admiral_pkg_versions()

Examples

admiral_pkg_versions()
#> admiral v1.2.0.9007, admiralonco v1.2.0, admiralophtha v1.2.0.9000, admiralvaccine v0.4.0, and admiralmetabolic v0.1.0
